  <brief_title>Preoperative Versus Postoperative Start With Thromboprophylaxis in THA (Total Hip Arthroplasty)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized, Double Blind Study to Evaluate Safety and Effect With Pre Versus Postoperative Start of Thromboprophylaxis With Dalteparin</official_title>
