  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if there are differences in clinical events, i.e
      bleeding with associated morbidity, if thromboprophylaxis with LMWH (Low Molecular Weight
      Heparin) is initiated before or after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
