    <intervention_type>Drug</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>dalteparin 5000 IU s.c.</intervention_name>
    <description>All patients receive injections with either 5000IU dalteparin or saline in the same volume the evening before surgery. All patients receive 5000IU dalteparin 6 hours after surgery and every day from day 2 until day 35.</description>
